trans-unit.source: A timer that is integrated into the <xref href="System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher"></xref> queue which is processed at a specified interval of time and at a specified priority.
trans-unit.target: En tidtaker som er integrert i den <xref href="System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher"> </xref> køen som er behandlet på et angitt tidsintervall og på en angitt prioritet.

trans-unit.source: The DispatcherTimer is reevaluated at the top of every <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher> loop.
Timers are not guaranteed to execute exactly when the time interval occurs, but they are guaranteed to not execute before the time interval occurs.
trans-unit.target: Tidtakerne garanteres ikke til å kjøre nøyaktig når tidsintervallet oppstår, men de garanteres du kan ikke kjøre før tidsintervallet forekommer.

trans-unit.source: This is because DispatcherTimer operations are placed on the <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher> queue like other operations.
trans-unit.target: Fordi DispatcherTimer operasjoner plasseres på den <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher>køen som andre operasjoner.</xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher>

trans-unit.source: When the DispatcherTimer operation executes is dependent on the other jobs in the queue and their priorities.
trans-unit.target: Når utfører operasjonen DispatcherTimer er avhengig av andre jobber i køen og tilhørende egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: If a <xref:System.Timers.Timer?displayProperty=fullName> is used in a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] application, it is worth noting that the <xref:System.Timers.Timer?displayProperty=fullName> runs on a different thread then the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] thread.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en <xref:System.Timers.Timer?displayProperty=fullName>er brukt i en [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] programmet, som det er verdt å merke seg som den <xref:System.Timers.Timer?displayProperty=fullName>kjører på en annen tråd vil [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] tråd.</xref:System.Timers.Timer?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Timers.Timer?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: In order to access objects on the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] thread, it is necessary to post the operation onto the <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher> of the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] thread using <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.Invoke%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.BeginInvoke%2A>.
trans-unit.target: For å få tilgang til objekter i den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] tråd, den kreves ikke poste operasjonen på den <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher>av den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] tråden ved hjelp av <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.Invoke%2A>eller <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.BeginInvoke%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.BeginInvoke%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher.Invoke%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher>

trans-unit.source: Reasons for using a DispatcherTimer opposed to a <xref:System.Timers.Timer?displayProperty=fullName> are that the DispatcherTimer runs on the same thread as the <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher> and a <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherPriority> can be set on the DispatcherTimer.
trans-unit.target: Grunner til å bruke en DispatcherTimer motsetning til en <xref:System.Timers.Timer?displayProperty=fullName>er DispatcherTimer kjører på samme tråd som den <xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher>og en <xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherPriority>kan angis for DispatcherTimer.</xref:System.Windows.Threading.DispatcherPriority> </xref:System.Windows.Threading.Dispatcher> </xref:System.Timers.Timer?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A DispatcherTimer will keep an object alive whenever the object's methods are bound to the timer.
trans-unit.target: En DispatcherTimer skal ha et objekt aktiv når objektets metoder er bundet til tidtakeren.
